data.title: Good root beer floats and....OK, that's pretty much it.
data.text: If you're hanquering for some good old fashioned root beer, or a root beer float the likes of which only A&W can make, look no further. If you're in the market for food. There are plenty of other good places to eat down the road. Shared with a KFC, I've never liked the poor quality of their food. My impression has been that they really don't care either.
